the supreme court today agreed to decide 
whether an indian tribe can prosecute members of other tribes for 
crimes on its reservation 
the court said it will review a ruling that gives the salt river 
pimamaricopa community in arizona authority to prosecute a 
california man accused in the fatal shooting of a 14year old boy 
