increase between 1986 and 1987 and a 6 percent jump between 1985 
and 1986 the report said 
the crime index records the number of selected crimes reported 
to state and local police agencies the fbi also tallies the number 
of burglaries larcenies motor vehicle thefts and arsons reported 
to authorities 
final tabulations for 1988 are expected to be released this 
summer the fbi said 
